Package com.natwest.opendata.service

Interface BaseOpenDataService<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ATMService, BCAService, BranchesService, CCCService, MetricsBCAService, MetricsPCAService, PCAService, SMEService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ATMServiceImpl, BCAServiceImpl, BranchesServiceImpl, CCCServiceImpl, MetricsBCAServiceImpl, MetricsPCAServiceImpl, PCAServiceImpl, SMEServiceImpl
    @Service
public interface BaseOpenDataService<T>
    This interface provide abstraction for other services like ATMService, BranchesService etc.

    Certain generic methods are present in interface that will be required for any of the implementation.

    For Example: getAllData(), exportAllDataAsCSV() etc.

    Other methods which are specific to the Service are defined in the sub interface.
